# Build context excludes — keep the context small and the build hermetic.
# The vulkanalia fork is cloned fresh in stage 1; the registry is filled from
# source; binaries + caches are produced inside the build, never shipped in.
**/target
**/.streamlib
# Per-package Cargo.lock files are gitignored dev artifacts; a stale one from a
# standalone `cargo` run under packages/* must not leak into the context and
# pin a dead source in the api-server resolution preflight. The tracked
# workspace-root Cargo.lock (not matched by this glob) still travels.
packages/**/Cargo.lock
.git
.github
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/_generated_
**/.venv
**/venv
**/*.slpkg
**/*.pyc
**/.mypy_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.DS_Store
docs/retests
*.log
